.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140740/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_remote-sprint-shifter-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140740/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_remote-sprint-shifter-700x420.jpg 700w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-263568\">mechanical or electronic shift compatible</figcaption></figure><p>While the electronic Powershift hub is shifted wirelessly, there isn’t direct integration (yet?) with <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=SRAM+eTap+AXS\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SRAM eTap AXS</a> shifter like there is with Di2 (Shimano shifters can plug directly into the Classified controller). But Classified provides their own sprint-style shifter button with every Powershift wheelset they sell that can be installed under the bar tape. So that means, you don’t even need an electronic shift derailleur.</p><p>Pretty much any modern 12mm thru-axle, flat mount disc brake, 11 or 12-speed derailleur equipped bike could be set up with a Classified Powershift system using one of their cassettes.</p><h3>Classified Powershift 12-speed – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3><figure id=\"attachment_263567\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-263567\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options.jpg\" alt=\"Classified Powershift 2x internal gear hub now SRAM 12-speed compatible,&nbsp;cassettes\" width=\"2000\" height=\"560\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-297x83.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-800x224.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-120x34.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-768x215.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-1536x430.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-696x195.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-1068x299.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-1920x538.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-1500x420.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-297x83.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-800x224.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-120x34.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-768x215.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-1536x430.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-696x195.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-1068x299.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-1920x538.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140734/Classified-Powershift-2x-internal-gear-hub-now-SRAM-12-speed-compatible_cassette-options-1500x420.jpg 1500w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-263567\">11-28, 11-30, 11-32 &amp; 11-34 gearing</figcaption></figure><p>The new 12-speed Classified cassettes will be available in 11-28, 11-30, 11-32 &amp; 11-34 gear ratios. They are paired with a traditional big ring up front, while the hub provides a 69% reduction gear inside. Since the cassettes do not go down to a 10T cog, like premium SRAM 12sp drivetrains, you’ll want to stick with a more conventional big ring in most cases to get you ideal gear ratios. Think 50-53T chainrings for road riding, and 46-50T rings for gravel, as a starting point.</p><figure id=\"attachment_249062\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-249062\"><a href=\"http://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set.jpg\" alt=\"Classified Carbon Wheelsets, gravel &amp; all-road wheels with wireless 2x internal gear hub built-in,&nbsp;30mm gravel\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Classified-Carbon-Wheelsets_gravel-all-road-wheels-with-wireless-2x-internal-gear-hub-built-in_30mm-set-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-249062\">30mm deep gravel wheels</figcaption></figure><p>Pre-order a new Classified 12-speed cassette now for 199€ (a bit more than the 175€ price if the 11-speed), and you can expect them to ship out starting in August. Of course, you’ll still need a <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/12/18/classified-adds-wheelsets-with-internal-gearing-so-you-can-double-the-range-of-your-current-1x-bike/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Classified Powershift equipped wheelset</a> which will set you back another 2400€ if you want to build up your own hidden 2×12 bike.</p><h3>European demo roadtrip</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140728/Classified-European-Vacation_Powershift-hub-dealer-road-trip.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140728/Classified-European-Vacation_Powershift-hub-dealer-road-trip.jpg\" alt=\"Classified Roadtrip, Classified Powershift European Vacation road trip\" width=\"1080\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140728/Classified-European-Vacation_Powershift-hub-dealer-road-trip.jpg 1080w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140728/Classified-Eur