.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140728/Classified-European-Vacation_Powershift-hub-dealer-road-trip-297x220.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140728/Classified-European-Vacation_Powershift-hub-dealer-road-trip-800x593.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140728/Classified-European-Vacation_Powershift-hub-dealer-road-trip-120x89.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140728/Classified-European-Vacation_Powershift-hub-dealer-road-trip-768x569.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140728/Classified-European-Vacation_Powershift-hub-dealer-road-trip-485x360.jpg 485w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140728/Classified-European-Vacation_Powershift-hub-dealer-road-trip-696x516.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140728/Classified-European-Vacation_Powershift-hub-dealer-road-trip-1068x791.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140728/Classified-European-Vacation_Powershift-hub-dealer-road-trip-567x420.jpg 567w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/30140728/Classified-European-Vacation_Powershift-hub-dealer-road-trip-80x60.jpg 80w\"></a></p><p>Classified is also in the process of dramatically ramping up their European production (<em>90% of their system is manufactured in BeNeLux</em>) and expanding their dealer service network in Europe. A couple of teams are driving around Europe this summer visiting bike shops to introduce them to the Powershift system in hopes of expanding from the current 60 shop network to a couple hundred by the end of the year. Bike shops can <a href=\"https://classified-cycling.cc/en/dealer-login\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">register their interest here</a> to schedule a stop from the roving Classified van.</p><p><a href=\"https://classified-cycling.cc/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>Classified-Cycling.cc</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"18f1e53fcfc4af182ecffbf5a19ad8ea8bd31bcc85e0e1f4bfc36d1d3b2608de","category":"Cycling"}